logger_name = OUTCOME_CONSTRAINT_PATH + '.logger'
with mock.patch(logger_name) as mock_warning:
    OutcomeConstraint(metric=self.minimize_metric, op=ComparisonOp.GEQ,
        bound=self.bound)
    mock_warning.warning.assert_called_once_with(CONSTRAINT_WARNING_MESSAGE
        .format(**LOWER_BOUND_MISMATCH))
with mock.patch(logger_name) as mock_warning:
    OutcomeConstraint(metric=self.maximize_metric, op=ComparisonOp.LEQ,
        bound=self.bound)
    mock_warning.warning.assert_called_once_with(CONSTRAINT_WARNING_MESSAGE
        .format(**UPPER_BOUND_MISMATCH))
